## â–¶ï¸ How to Run the Project

### Step 1: Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/sarika70/flask_app.git
cd flask_app
```

### Step 2: Install Requirements (if needed)

```bash
pip install flask
```

### Step 3: Run Any Flask App

Example:

```bash
cd 01_simple
python app.py
```

Then open in browser:

```
http://127.0.0.1:5000/
```

